prodNameC: 免疫特 鐵蛋白試劑
ingredientsDesc:
Ferritin Test Units(LFE1)
Each barcode-labeled unit contains one bead coated with monoclonal murine anti-ferritin.
Ferritin Reagent Wedge(LFE2)
6.5mL alkaline phosphatase(bovine calf intestine) conjugated to polyclonal goat anti-derritin in buffer.
Ferritin Adjustors(LFEL.LFEH)
Two vials (Low and High), 2.5mL each, of ferritin in a human protein-based matrix.
Ferritin Sample Diluent (LFEZ): One vial containing 25 mL of a ferritin-free human protein-based matrix, with preservative.
applicantName: 西門子醫療設備股份有限公司

efficacy: 供IMMULITE分析儀用於體外診斷，定量檢測血清中鐵蛋白含量，對鐵元素缺乏症和鐵超負荷的診斷起輔助作用。
